objects

Class Route

  • java.lang.Object
    • objects.Route

  • public class Route
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represents set of TimeStamps which are going to be visited on the way to target and to home by ship with this Route. Provides tools for creating route for ship and setting actions to individual TimeStamps on this route
    Author:
    Martin Hamet
